Syntax Highlighting ​

VitePress provides Syntax Highlighting powered by Shiki, with additional features like line-highlighting:

Input

md
```js{4}
export default {
  data () {
    return {
      msg: 'Highlighted!'
    }
  }
}
```

Output

js
export default {
  data () {
    return {
      msg: 'Highlighted!'
    }
  }
}
